OL,3,CMan dies after blaze inside Belfast
OL,4,Chospital's emergency department
OL,6,FA man has died after a fire at the
OL,7,FRoyal Victoria Hospital on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fpolice have confirmed.
OL,10,FThe Fire and Rescue Service was called
OL,11,Fto the blaze, which started in a
OL,12,Fbathroom on the ground floor, just
OL,13,Fbefore seven o'clock yesterday evening.
OL,15,FA man in his 30s was taken into care
OL,16,Fat the hospital but has since sadly
OL,17,Fpassed away.
OL,19,FThe PSNI have confirmed that the death
OL,20,Fis currently being treated as sudden
OL,21,Fand is not considered suspicious.
